column5: this was reported this morning on the radio  A Tourist Camp in Waldof has been completely destroyed following an early morning fire Thursday. Machin, Dryden and Oxdrift fire crews were dispatched around 3 o'clock. Firefighters spent in excess of 4-hours battling the blaze. Machin Fire Chief Rob Wisneski says no one was injured. Wisneski adds the cause is under investigation. The name of the camp has not yet been released by Fire Officials.
Bear Trail Lodge maybe? Andy Myers? Glad no one was hurt.
Copied and pasted from another site
